OL,3,CEmergency measures brought in to ease
OL,4,Cprison overcrowding as rioters
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FThe government has triggered a plan to
OL,8,Fease overcrowding in prisons, as more
OL,9,Frioters are being sentenced for their
OL,10,Frole in recent unrest, ITV News'
OL,11,FPolitical Correspondent Harry Horton
OL,12,Freports.
OL,14,FThe government has activated emergency
OL,15,Fmeasures to avoid prison overcrowding
OL,16,Fin the North of England as more
OL,17,Frioters are sentenced.
