OL,3,CEmergency measures brought in to ease
OL,4,Cprison overcrowding as rioters
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FOperation Early Dawn, a long-standing
OL,8,Fplan that allows defendants to be held
OL,9,Fin police cells and not summoned to
OL,10,Fmagistrates' court until a space in
OL,11,Fprison is available, was activated on
OL,12,FMonday morning, the Ministry of
OL,13,FJustice said.
OL,15,FThe measures will be put in place in
OL,16,Fthe North East and Yorkshire; Cumbria
OL,17,Fand Lancashire; and Manchester,
OL,18,FMerseyside and Cheshire regions.
