OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FOn a visit to Northern Ireland, Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer was asked
OL,9,Fwhether Operation Early Dawn posed a
OL,10,Frisk to public safety, in respect of
OL,11,Fpolicing resources being diverted or
OL,12,Fprisoners being bailed when they
OL,13,Fotherwise would not be.
OL,15,F"Well, these decisions are really
OL,16,Ftough decisions, and nobody wants to
OL,17,Ftake them, they are difficult
OL,18,Fdecisions," he told reporters at the
OL,19,FPSNI's training college in Belfast.
