OL,3,CEmergency measures brought in to ease
OL,4,Cprison overcrowding as rioters
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,F"They are having to be taken for one
OL,8,Freason and one reason only, and that
OL,9,Fis the terrible inheritance on prisons
OL,10,Fthat we had as an incoming government
OL,11,Ffrom the previous government.
OL,13,F"There was a basic failure, which is a
OL,14,Ffailure to have enough prison places
OL,15,Ffor the number of prisoners that were
OL,16,Fbeing sentenced to prison...
