OL,3,CEmergency measures brought in to ease
OL,4,Cprison overcrowding as rioters
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,F"But, as I hope we've been able to
OL,8,Fdemonstrate, we've taken tough
OL,9,Fdecisions, we've been able to prove
OL,10,Fthat if you commit disorder, you can
OL,11,Fexpect to be put through the criminal
OL,12,Fjustice system quickly, and we will
OL,13,Fcontinue in that vein. But I'm not
OL,14,Fgoing to pretend that this isn't a
OL,15,Fchallenge. We will take the necessary
OL,16,Ftough decisions on this, but we should
OL,17,Fnever, ever have been put in the
OL,18,Fposition that we're in today."
