OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FPressed on a potential risk to public
OL,8,Fsafety, he replied: "We are managing
OL,9,Fthat risk and of course these are
OL,10,Ftough decisions, but I think you've
OL,11,Fseen over the last two or three weeks
OL,12,Fthe way in which we've approached
OL,13,Fthis, which is to make sure that any
OL,14,Frisk is mitigated, to make sure we do
OL,15,Fhave the spaces available for the
OL,16,Fprisoners that we need to be held in
OL,17,Fprison."
