OL,7,FAuthorities could trigger and
OL,8,Fdeactivate emergency plans to ease
OL,9,Fprison overcrowding in northern
OL,10,FEngland several times over the next
OL,11,Ffew weeks, suggested a Downing Street
OL,12,Fspokesperson.
OL,14,FShe said she expects the area will
OL,15,F"move in and out of" Operation Early
OL,16,FDawn during "short periods of
OL,17,Fsignificant pressure".
