OL,7,FShe said: "It is a pre-existing
OL,8,Fcontingency measure that is used for
OL,9,Fshort periods ` a matter of days or
OL,10,Fweeks to manage immediate, localised
OL,11,Fpressures on the prison estate."
OL,13,FNational Police Chiefs' Council
OL,14,Fcustody lead Deputy Chief Constable
OL,15,FNev Kemp added: "We are working
OL,16,Fclosely with criminal justice system
OL,17,Fpartners to manage demand in the
OL,18,Fsystem and ensure that the public are
OL,19,Fsafe.
