OL,3,CEmergency measures brought in to ease
OL,4,Cprison overcrowding as rioters
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FAfter the riots that broke out across
OL,8,FEngland following the stabbing of
OL,9,Fthree girls in Southport, a total of
OL,10,F460 people had appeared in
OL,11,Fmagistrates' courts in relation to the
OL,12,Fdisorder by the end of Thursday.
OL,14,FOperation Early Dawn was previously
OL,15,Ftriggered by the Conservative
OL,16,Fgovernment in May in a bid to tackle
OL,17,Fovercrowding in jails.
