OL,3,CEmergency measures brought in to ease
OL,4,Cprison overcrowding as rioters
OL,5,Csentenced
OL,7,FLast month, the Ministry of Justice
OL,8,Fsaid violence and self-harm in prison
OL,9,Fhad risen to "unacceptable" levels as
OL,10,Fovercrowding pushed jails to the
OL,11,F"point of collapse".
OL,13,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,14,Fannounced plans to cut the proportion
OL,15,Fof the sentence inmates must serve
OL,16,Fbehind bars from 50% to 40%.
